comments: He is a nice teacher. He knows his subject very well. His explanations are excellent, and his classes are a lot of fun. If you want to learn English, take him.

He is a great teacher!!! You can learn a lot from him. His teaching methodology is very interesting. If you study and attend classes you should do well. I took his classes twice and got As. His classes are fun! Bonga-Bonga! Very helpful teacher! Highly recommended!
